  Config
  Choose a focused config.toml settings section.

› 1. Account & automation    Auth failover, usage resets, recaps, and update policy. 7
                             settings.
  2. Self-healing            Automatic recovery from usage and model availability
                             errors. 4 settings.
  3. AI context              What Codewith shows the model. 5 settings.
  4. Interface & privacy     Composer, transcript, privacy, and TUI behavior. 8
                             settings.
  5. Agent subagent threads  Max concurrent subagent threads per agent run (currently
                             the built-in default).
  6. Goal objective limit    Max characters echoed per goal objective (now 4000).

  Press enter to open; esc to close
